Frequently Asked Questions

Can Supportics handle high volumes of customer inquiries?▼
Yes, Supportics is equipped to manage high volumes of customer inquiries efficiently through its various support channels, including Live Chat, Phone Answering, and Email Support.
Will my customers notice they're talking to an outsourced team?▼
YNo, Supportics ensures that all agents are well-trained and familiar with your company's policies and products, providing seamless and professional customer interactions.
How quickly can Supportics start supporting my customers?▼
Supportics can begin supporting your customers shortly after the initial setup and onboarding process, which is designed to be quick and efficient.
Can I monitor the performance of the outsourced customer support?▼
Yes, Supportics provides detailed performance reports and analytics, allowing you to monitor the effectiveness and quality of the customer support services.
How will Supportics understand my offerings?▼
Supportics conducts thorough training sessions and works closely with you to understand your products, services, and customer interaction requirements, ensuring accurate and helpful support..
Is my information secure with Supportics?▼
Yes, Supportics prioritizes data security and employs stringent measures to protect your information, ensuring confidentiality and compliance with relevant regulations.
How do I get the chat working on my website?▼
Supportics provides a simple integration process with detailed instructions to get the live chat feature up and running on your website.
What happens after the free trial with Supportics?▼
After the free trial, you can choose from various support packages offered by Supportics based on your needs and continue benefiting from their services without interruption.
Do you offer an account manager, and what is their role?▼
Yes, Supportics assigns an account manager to each client. The account manager's role is to ensure smooth communication, address any concerns, and help optimize the support services provided..
Can I self-chat with my website visitors using Supportics?▼
Yes, Supportics allows you to interact directly with your website visitors through the chat feature if you prefer to manage certain interactions personally.
